{"tid":327610,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誠品創辦人吳清友心臟病發猝逝　終年68歲 (22:46)","createTime":"2017-07-19T01:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T10:08:22.000Z","uid":22675,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ec21e37d6e838946c4d57d7745cdfb8b47fcf100","tid":327610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T01:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170718/s00004/5d3f1754b8d8398d4319cb7458f53131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170718%2Fs00004%2F5d3f1754b8d8398d4319cb7458f53131.jpg&h=6ce68509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2017/7/18<br />\n<br />\n 共1幅  上一頁下一頁 <br />\n誠品書店創辦人吳清友今日晚上在台北病逝，終年68歲。吳清友患有先天性心臟擴大症，誠品稱他因心臟舊疾辭世。台灣傳媒報道，吳昨日仍前往視察台北新建成的中山地下書街「誠品R79」，後日有新書發布會，惟今日晚上7時多突然病發送院，但抵達時已無呼吸心跳。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n誠品在晚上9時半公布消息，表示將召開臨時董事會推舉董事長，又指公司遵循代理人作業，各項業務均由專業經理人負責，對公司營運無影響。<br />\n<br />\n吳清友患有先天性心臟擴大症，1988年做過第一次開胸心臟手術，生前一共做過3次大手術。他於1989年3月創辦誠品書店，初期專賣藝術與建築類書籍，至1999年誠品敦南店首開24小時營業，結合書店與商場，建立別具一格的誠品書店文化。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社/自由時報）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170718/s00004/1500388535664\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170718%2Fs00004%2F1500388535664&d=5J%2Fsy652tLXeL1eugdBMVBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=fc1d4313\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170718%2Fs00004%2F1500388535664&h=dfbdb315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170718/s00004/1500388535664</a>"},{"pid":"7fe394afe2e4d4b11adffeb7ed16a8faa9a51f5f","tid":327610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:46:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d063a56856b263aec8b485ea6c8cec8c01ea8a9","tid":327610,"uid":32511,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T02:51:03.000Z","msg":"好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書嘅人支持言論出版審查，做人忘本抵俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b4857be0a1973b37db165fd8d9fb0599d14146","tid":327610,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T06:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書嘅人支持言論出版審查，做人忘本抵俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來今日心情好差 而家睇到依篇新聞 心情愉快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6860928dd85ae45e6faac8459d4c3cda0a5d12d6","tid":327610,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n賣書嘅人支持言論出版審查，做人忘本抵俾天收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本來今日心情好差 而家睇到依篇新聞 心情愉快 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab6c6c2825840cc83901dc89c108505f764496a3","tid":327610,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"[url]訪問梁天琦新書　誠品拒入貨 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/313075/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/313075/page/1?ref=ios</a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區[/url]<br />\n<br />\n如果一種唸法大部份人都覺得係唔work，唔需要俾壓力，自然會收檔。因為是否接受一個人寫嘅野，關鍵係讀者是否認同作者嘅唸法。<br />\n<br />\n希特拉嘅思想雖然危險，西方出板社一樣出板到，讀者一樣可以買到我的奮鬥，皆因支那範圍外有出板同言論自由。是否讚同其思想係讀者嘅選擇。<br />\n<br />\n如果以為單靠禁書/唔賣就可以打壓思想，係一個好低能嘅唸法。"},{"pid":"df463a9c91637832a3680bdd11fc095696a17237","tid":327610,"uid":119778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:47:53.000Z","msg":"抵啦死台狗"},{"pid":"e18463c40a7e37dcaeb79e1ba7012dd7f1c09565","tid":327610,"uid":39277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T07:54:00.000Z","msg":"睇錯咗名創優品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6ab84487be214fba6bee3fcf2f4bb09e0e9b45","tid":327610,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:35:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯咗名創優品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果係嘅話都唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eedae88ac8a7f55e95e30732825a1138bfbd1f51","tid":327610,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"冇計啦 俾天收 70大壽都過唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a142e92a1ea556f392c246d739c93c978414ae","tid":327610,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T10:08:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇計啦 俾天收 70大壽都過唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲要趕唔切上海誠品開幕"}]}